data.description: Welcome to this move-in-ready quaint 3 bedroom, 1 bath, ranch home. This home features completely renovated kitchen with granite counter tops, cabinetry, and pendant lighting! The bathroom has also been totally remodeled from top to bottom with a walk-in tiled shower with glass door. Newer electric, plumbing, and windows. Fully fenced yard that stretches to back alleyway. Close proximity to Hyde Park, Sal Maglie Stadium, Golf Course, and Little Italy on Pine. Seller is accepting offers as they are submitted.
